Deployement:

- Azure Deployment Center in Azure Functions:
Configurable to be uploaded from github, bitbucket, git local/external repo, dropbox, oneDrive, Azure Devops

- Zip it and upload it with Azure CLI or by using a REST interface 

Unit testing:

Create a new xUnitTests project

Download Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc nuGet pacakge -> this creates a mock http environment
